 THE FILTER (Size Constraint)**\n    *   Single-character words resulting from splits, such as 'እና' and 'ም', were discarded as per the protocol requiring words to be at least 2 characters long.","input_words":["በላኩባቸው","የሚያስተረጉሙለት","ፕላውንዴን","እንዲያጠኑትና","ወደሚያርፉባት","ላስለምዳት","ሊነሡ","የብልሹዎችንም","መጃጀታቸው","ይከፈልላቸዋል","ለባለሀብቶቹም","ሙየቶችም","የሚያጠናክርልኝን","አደኩኝ","የፈጁትን","የተሸንፈውን","ካርበኖች","አስክሬንህ","እያለፈኝ","እየረጨኝ","የኰንዶሚኒየም","በተከራየሁዋት","አዳብዬው","የባሰኝ","ስለሰበሰብክ","ስላፈረስክ","ተባባሪህ","ተጠቀምኩና","ቻሪቲም","ከምናተኩር"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"52afc450-1e50-46b5-bbc0-dcb041796cf7","created_at":"2026-03-03T22:09:13.563369+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_14/chunk_0556.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Noun","root":"ፍልም","word":"ፍልም","synonyms":["film","movie","cinema"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኢትዮጵያ","word":"ኢትዮጵያ","synonyms":["Ethiopia"],"importance":9},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መቻል","word":"ቻላችሁ","synonyms":["to be able","to be capable","to manage","to succeed"],"importance":8},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ዐዋቂ","word":"ዐዋቂዎች","synonyms":["expert","knowledgeable person","wise person","scholar"],"importance":8},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መሠልጠን","word":"የሠለጠናሁ","synonyms":["to be trained","to be civilized","to be educated","to be refined"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ፋና","word":"ፋናውን","synonyms":["torch","light","beacon","guide","path"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ፍልም","word":"ፈልሞችን","synonyms":["film","movie","cinema"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ማስረጃ","word":"አስረጅ","synonyms":["evidence","proof","demonstrator","witness"],"importance":8},{"pos":"Noun","root":"መከላከል","word":"መካለያ","synonyms":["defense","protection","shield","barrier","means of defense"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መጣል","word":"ተጥሎልኛል","synonyms":["to throw","to drop","to cast","to abandon"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መጋጨት","word":"ማጋጨት","synonyms":["to clash","to collide","to cause conflict","to make confront"],"impor